{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/Re-Mind_title_animation.gif?t=1737691272\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Master Your Memory!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into the ultimate memory challenge with over 1,000 unique cards! This isn't your average matching game \u2013 it's a brain-teasing adventure that will keep you coming back for more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/Card_Flip_4.gif?t=1737691272\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83c\udfae Your Game, Your Way</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Three Game Modes:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf38 Cozy Mode - Relax and play at your own pace</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u23f1\ufe0f Normal Mode - Test your skills against the clock</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfc6 Challenge Mode - Race the clock while matching cards in deceptively similar colors!</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Customizable Difficulty Levels</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/Board_Sizes.png?t=1737691272\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83c\udfa8 Endless Customization</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>20 Stunning Card Styles</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>30 Beautiful Backgrounds</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Selection of Music choices</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock new looks with in-game currency earned through play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No microtransactions \u2013 everything is earned through gameplay!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/Card_styles_showcase.gif?t=1737691272\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udcda 8 Themed Card Packs</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mix and match from these diverse collections:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfaf Activities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83e\udd81 Animals and Nature</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf55 Food and Drink</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfae Objects</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\ude04 Smileys and People</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2b50 Symbols</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf0d Travel and Places</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf8c Flags</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/Card_packs.gif?t=1737691272\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83c\udfc6 Features That Keep You Coming Back</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Improve Your Memory - See real improvements in your memory over time, trackable with the... :</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Steam Leaderboards - Test your memory against other players worldwide! \ud83d\udcaa\ud83e\udde0\ud83e\udd47</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Achievements - Over 20 challenging goals to unlock</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Earn Stars - Unlock new content through gameplay</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Challenge mode - Put your memory to the test with this color specific mode!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/Challenge_mode.png?t=1737691272\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udcab Perfect For:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Brain training enthusiasts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Casual gamers looking for a challenge</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Young gamers - Build focus, concentration, and cognitive skills while having fun! Perfect for parents looking for engaging educational gaming</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players who love customization</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Achievement hunters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Anyone looking to improve their memory skills</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/Card_Flip_1.gif?t=1737691272\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play now and put your memory to the test! \ud83c\udfaf</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udc8c A Note from the Developer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Originally a beloved 'Dreams' creation on the PS4, this memory game has been completely rebuilt and enhanced for Steam with new features, stunning visuals, and extended customization options. The community's enthusiasm for the Dreams version inspired me to bring this polished experience to PC players!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Speed Runner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3297240/7502281270333fdbb413d15e03949875fdc9b0a1.jpg"},{"name":"Memory Novice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3297240/e9737eb3b80eb3f30799a9fc76cf7385076e7079.jpg"},{"name":"First Pair","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3297240/8fad9d06d23e8b95c3f5f0897a6dd4bed3600dbc.jpg"},{"name":"Memory Prodigy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3297240/21bdb9bbe3903c06f714a23ae9c697fa27467900.jpg"},{"name":"Memory Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3297240/9c0ef0db58702547efbac86ebb209f082f4bfbcc.jpg"},{"name":"Match Streak","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcom